halla bol ( raise your voice ) is an indian hindi drama film released on 11 january 2008 , and directed by rajkumar santoshi . halla bol stars ajay devgan and vidya balan in pivotal roles and a number of celebrities from the hindi film industry appear as themselves . produced by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; siddiqui , the film 's score and soundtrack was composed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; singh , while &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and steven bernard were the cinematographer and editor respectively . the film touches upon the jessica lall murder case , aamir khan 's involvement with the narmada &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; andolan , the right to information act , and public participation in fighting corruption . it also references the theatre group jan &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , whose leader , theatre activist safdar hashmi , was killed by political rivals while performing a street play by the same name , halla bol ! , in 1989 .